[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

113
00:14:44,340 --> 00:14:46,740
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, koji su povezani Sovjetskim establishmentu, oni su sovjetskim,

114
00:14:46,740 --> 00:14:48,399
[SPEAKER_01] mislim, obeštenim službama, ali...

115
00:14:48,399 --> 00:14:54,100
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, bili su povezani sa režimom totalitarnim i onda su se transformirali u kapitalizam.

116
00:14:54,100 --> 00:14:58,559
[SPEAKER_01] E, ovaj slučaj, na primjer, prije rata u Ukrajina, imate 2001 tu intervenciju

117
00:14:58,559 --> 00:15:03,500
[SPEAKER_01] koji je Putin napravio u Kazahstanu, kako bi se čuvao kazahstanski režim od te pobune.

118
00:15:03,500 --> 00:15:08,360
[SPEAKER_01] Znamo da je Kazahstan jedna zemlja koja se, onako, dosta dobro ekonomski razvija,

119
00:15:08,360 --> 00:15:12,100
[SPEAKER_01] s obzirom na nema, dakle, ima dobre, te prirodne resurse,

120
00:15:12,620 --> 00:15:14,840
[SPEAKER_01] i tamo je postao neki pokušaj...

121
00:15:14,840 --> 00:15:15,940
[SPEAKER_01] Osamostaljenja, tako.

122
00:15:15,940 --> 00:15:21,559
[SPEAKER_01] ...otpora i taj otpor je odmah sredan u startu, a predsjednik Kazahstana,

123
00:15:21,559 --> 00:15:24,580
[SPEAKER_01] koji je pozvalo pomoć Putina, vidi kako pogledate njegovu biografiju,

124
00:15:24,580 --> 00:15:27,559
[SPEAKER_01] on je obitišao u Moskovske škole diplomacije.

125
00:15:27,559 --> 00:15:28,080
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

126
00:15:28,080 --> 00:15:30,879
[SPEAKER_01] I on je izravan, dakle, to je taj stari utjecaj koji...

127
00:15:30,879 --> 00:15:34,559
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to su u stvari suradnici režima Sovjetskog iz vremena...

128
00:15:34,559 --> 00:15:37,200
[SPEAKER_01] Iz vremena koji danas u novim prilikama, dakle...

129
00:15:37,200 --> 00:15:43,120
[SPEAKER_01] Da, mislim, ne demokracija, čak to su diktature u kojima...

130
00:15:43,120 --> 00:15:45,840
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem, i ono što je bio problem u Ukrajine, konkretan problem,

131
00:15:45,840 --> 00:15:52,919
[SPEAKER_01] što u Ukrajine nije taj model, politički model, autokratski model iz Moskve.

132
00:15:52,919 --> 00:15:55,179
[SPEAKER_01] Nije jednostavno mogao biti presađen. Zašto?

133
00:15:55,179 --> 00:15:57,580
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto Ukrajina ima drugačiju povijest,

134
00:15:57,580 --> 00:16:03,360
[SPEAKER_01] ima drugačiju tu te regionalne odnose,

135
00:16:03,360 --> 00:16:06,860
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, ima i vjerski izraz do podijenja zemlja,

136
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:10,100
[SPEAKER_01] imate Grko-katolike, pa imate, na primjer, tri pravoslavne crkve.

137
00:16:10,100 --> 00:16:13,840
[SPEAKER_01] Jedna koja prizvane Moskovskog patriarka,

138
00:16:13,840 --> 00:16:16,779
[SPEAKER_01] imate ovu Ukrajinsku crku koja je nastala nakon 1991,

139
00:16:16,779 --> 00:16:18,700
[SPEAKER_01] imate Ukrajinsku crku koja je došla iz emigracije,

140
00:16:18,700 --> 00:16:19,779
[SPEAKER_01] razumite, dakle, imate...

141
00:16:19,779 --> 00:16:20,960
[SPEAKER_00] Tri pravoslavne crkve.

142
00:16:20,960 --> 00:16:24,519
[SPEAKER_01] Imate Grko-katolike, onda imate i, dakle,

143
00:16:24,519 --> 00:16:27,799
[SPEAKER_01] postoji ta Ruska manjina nacionalna,

144
00:16:27,799 --> 00:16:30,879
[SPEAKER_01] koja je borini 17%, tako da je to jedna zemlja koja onako...

145
00:16:30,879 --> 00:16:33,379
[SPEAKER_00] A Ruska manjina ima, koliko si rekla, 17%?

146
00:16:33,379 --> 00:16:35,279
[SPEAKER_01] Imala je do rata 2014...

147
00:16:35,279 --> 00:16:39,419
[SPEAKER_00] I sada je Ukrajinskoj pravoslavnoj crkvi priznata autokefalnost,

148
00:16:39,419 --> 00:16:40,600
[SPEAKER_00] ili nije?

149
00:16:40,600 --> 00:16:43,700
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne, ne, ne, imate, dakle, imate Ukrajinsku crku.

150
00:16:43,700 --> 00:16:44,360
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

151
00:16:44,360 --> 00:16:47,759
[SPEAKER_01] Ukrajinskoj crkvi je priznata 2019.

152
00:16:47,759 --> 00:16:50,059
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, Bartolomej, ovaj crkarski padre,

153
00:16:50,059 --> 00:16:52,240
[SPEAKER_01] on je priznao, dakle, u sukobu s Moskovom,

154
00:16:52,240 --> 00:16:54,919
[SPEAKER_01] to je taj još jedan sukob u pravoslavnom svijetu,

155
00:16:54,919 --> 00:16:57,639
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, priznanje Ukrajinske pravoslavne crkve,

156
00:16:57,639 --> 00:17:01,539
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, koja je nastala nakon pada Sovjetskog savjeza.

157
00:17:01,539 --> 00:17:02,960
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon 90. godina, tako je.

158
00:17:02,960 --> 00:17:04,559
[SPEAKER_01] Imate Ukrajinsku crkvu koja je bila u imigraciji.

159
00:17:04,559 --> 00:17:05,180
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro.

160
00:17:05,180 --> 00:17:06,539
[SPEAKER_01] I koja je nastala svoj rad.

161
00:17:06,539 --> 00:17:09,900
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, izvan Sovjetskog savjeza.

162
00:17:09,900 --> 00:17:10,819
[SPEAKER_01] Izvan došla iz imigracije.

163
00:17:10,819 --> 00:17:14,799
[SPEAKER_01] I imate ovu koja je i dalje ostala lojalna Ukrajinska crkva,

164
00:17:14,799 --> 00:17:17,359
[SPEAKER_01] koja je lojalna Moskovskoj patriaršije.

165
00:17:17,359 --> 00:17:21,019
[SPEAKER_01] Imate tri pravoslavne crkve.

166
00:17:21,019 --> 00:17:25,180
[SPEAKER_01] I kažem, to je veliki spor koji je nastala u pravoslavnom svijetu

167
00:17:25,180 --> 00:17:27,859
[SPEAKER_01] i nastala su veliki sukobi upravo oko priznanja,

168
00:17:27,859 --> 00:17:34,079
[SPEAKER_01] jer je vaseljanski patriarh Bartolomej crkve da priznao

169
00:17:34,079 --> 00:17:35,319
[SPEAKER_01] Ukrajinsku pravoslavnu crkvu.

170
00:17:35,319 --> 00:17:38,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo koja je nastala nakon 1990. godina.

171
00:17:38,619 --> 00:17:39,420
[SPEAKER_01] I to je veliki problem.

172
00:17:39,420 --> 00:17:42,859
[SPEAKER_00] To je veliki problem i za Mosko, odnosno za pravoslavnu crku.

173
00:17:42,859 --> 00:17:47,480
[SPEAKER_01] Uglavnom, Srpska pravoslana crkva i Ruska pravoslana crkva

174
00:17:47,480 --> 00:17:52,039
[SPEAKER_01] su najžešće u tome, protiv toga priznanja,

175
00:17:52,039 --> 00:17:55,680
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, autokefalna su Ukrajinske crkve bile nakon 2019. godine.

176
00:17:55,680 --> 00:18:01,299
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, i sad ovo što si rekao, vezano za taj sukob,

177
00:18:01,299 --> 00:18:04,259
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, za rat između Rusije i Ukrajine,

178
00:18:04,259 --> 00:18:07,859
[SPEAKER_00] osim ovog sad religioznog elementa,

179
00:18:07,859 --> 00:18:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno pravoslavnog sukoba,

180
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:13,299
[SPEAKER_00] koji potiče iz 2019. imamo ovaj ekonomski,

181
00:18:13,299 --> 00:18:15,720
[SPEAKER_00] u kojem su Ukrajinske željeli...

182
00:18:15,720 --> 00:18:18,819
[SPEAKER_01] Da, to je u biti jedan oblik socijalne revolucije,

183
00:18:18,819 --> 00:18:20,400
[SPEAKER_01] jedna borba za dva ekonomskog modela,

184
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:21,640
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, Ukrajinske žele živiti u jednom,

185
00:18:21,640 --> 00:18:24,079
[SPEAKER_01] žele jedan ekonomski model koji neće biti,

186
00:18:24,079 --> 00:18:26,140
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, taj oligarhijski,

187
00:18:26,140 --> 00:18:29,700
[SPEAKER_01] u biti imate, politički imate autokraciju

188
00:18:29,700 --> 00:18:30,819
[SPEAKER_01] i plus oligarhiju.

189
00:18:30,819 --> 00:18:31,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ekonomsku oligarhiju, da.

190
00:18:31,819 --> 00:18:34,599
[SPEAKER_01] Oligarhiju, dakle, to su dva ispripetena sistema

191
00:18:34,599 --> 00:18:37,500
[SPEAKER_01] koje su nastale, dakle, u tom specifičnom ruskom kapitalizmu

192
00:18:37,500 --> 00:18:39,799
[SPEAKER_01] koji se razvija nakon 1990. godine.

193
00:18:39,799 --> 00:18:43,519
[SPEAKER_00] Koji, u principu, otežava stvaranje slobodnog tržišta

194
00:18:43,519 --> 00:18:45,940
[SPEAKER_00] i pravedno natjecanje u ekonomiji,

195
00:18:45,940 --> 00:18:47,900
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, tvrtki, firmi, svega.

196
00:18:47,900 --> 00:18:49,279
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to su te stare strukture,

197
00:18:49,279 --> 00:18:50,400
[SPEAKER_01] monopolističke strukture,

198
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:52,539
[SPEAKER_01] koje su izašle iz toga sovjetskog establišmenta,

199
00:18:52,539 --> 00:18:54,259
[SPEAKER_01] koje jednostavno dopuštaju,

200
00:18:54,259 --> 00:18:56,160
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, ovo što ih kajte,

201
00:18:56,160 --> 00:18:59,619
[SPEAKER_01] te tržišne ideje,

202
00:18:59,619 --> 00:19:05,880
[SPEAKER_01] jer one žele kontrolirati sve ekonomske procese,

203
00:19:05,880 --> 00:19:08,299
[SPEAKER_01] svako odmicanje od toga,

204
00:19:08,299 --> 00:19:11,500
[SPEAKER_01] znači, doboćenju pitanje autokratskog modela,

205
00:19:11,500 --> 00:19:14,460
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno političke kontrole ekonomije,

206
00:19:14,460 --> 00:19:17,559
[SPEAKER_00] a to je bila značika komunističkog sustava,

207
00:19:17,559 --> 00:19:21,079
[SPEAKER_00] da je politika, partija je kontrolirala ekonomiju.

208
00:19:21,079 --> 00:19:23,059
[SPEAKER_01] Imajte tu naivnost na zapadu,

209
00:19:23,059 --> 00:19:24,819
[SPEAKER_01] to je taj naivnost koja vlada na zapadu,

210
00:19:24,819 --> 00:19:25,960
[SPEAKER_01] da vi možete, na primjer,

211
00:19:25,960 --> 00:19:28,279
[SPEAKER_01] možete imati te tranše ekonomske s Rusijom,

212
00:19:28,279 --> 00:19:32,859
[SPEAKER_01] ali ruski oligarci nisu obični podzetnici,

213
00:19:32,859 --> 00:19:34,480
[SPEAKER_01] koji su nastali slobodno tržište.

214
00:19:34,480 --> 00:19:37,339
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su ljudi koji su pod izranom kontrolom Kremlja

215
00:19:37,339 --> 00:19:39,259
[SPEAKER_01] i njihove investicije na zapadu,

216
00:19:39,259 --> 00:19:41,119
[SPEAKER_01] pa oni su investirali,

217
00:19:41,119 --> 00:19:42,960
[SPEAKER_01] oni su kupili Španijansku obalu, Italijansku,

218
00:19:42,960 --> 00:19:44,299
[SPEAKER_01] kod nas su dožli novice, kod nas.

219
00:19:44,299 --> 00:19:45,940
[SPEAKER_00] Su vezane uvijek za politiku.

220
00:19:45,940 --> 00:19:48,980
[SPEAKER_01] E, i svi te ekonomske akcije

221
00:19:48,980 --> 00:19:51,420
[SPEAKER_01] su duboko politički, imaju duboko političku posadnje.

222
00:19:51,420 --> 00:19:54,619
[SPEAKER_01] I ovoga, tako da te ruske investicije su,

223
00:19:54,619 --> 00:19:57,640
[SPEAKER_01] kažem, zapad je prihvatio,

224
00:19:57,640 --> 00:19:58,640
[SPEAKER_01] to je onaj problem,

225
00:19:58,640 --> 00:20:00,720
[SPEAKER_01] jer to je onaj problem sukoba s Kinom,

226
00:20:00,720 --> 00:20:05,559
[SPEAKER_01] američko-kinijenski sukob ekonomski,

227
00:20:05,559 --> 00:20:06,319
[SPEAKER_01] jednostavno što imate vi,

228
00:20:06,319 --> 00:20:07,940
[SPEAKER_01] dakle imate dva modela ekonomska

229
00:20:07,940 --> 00:20:09,059
[SPEAKER_01] koje trebaju sorađivati,

230
00:20:09,059 --> 00:20:11,140
[SPEAKER_01] sad imate ovaj američki koji zastupa

231
00:20:11,140 --> 00:20:12,160
[SPEAKER_01] tu trčničnu poziciju,

232
00:20:12,160 --> 00:20:13,980
[SPEAKER_01] imate ovaj zatvoren sistem,

233
00:20:13,980 --> 00:20:15,779
[SPEAKER_01] kontrolirani sistem u Rusiji i Kini,

234
00:20:15,779 --> 00:20:17,519
[SPEAKER_01] i sad kako ćete vi raditi ekonomsku razmiju?

235
00:20:17,519 --> 00:20:18,559
[SPEAKER_01] To je taj problem.

236
00:20:18,980 --> 00:20:21,279
[SPEAKER_01] da kineske kompanije mogu bez problema

237
00:20:21,279 --> 00:20:22,599
[SPEAKER_01] raditi na američkom tržištu,

238
00:20:22,599 --> 00:20:24,059
[SPEAKER_01] dok američke kompanije ne mogu

239
00:20:24,059 --> 00:20:25,759
[SPEAKER_01] slovo natjeći na kineskom tržištu.

240
00:20:25,759 --> 00:20:27,099
[SPEAKER_01] Imaju razna graničenja.

241
00:20:27,099 --> 00:20:29,119
[SPEAKER_01] I to je ozbiljan problem.

242
00:20:29,119 --> 00:20:30,599
[SPEAKER_01] Jednostavno, mi ne možete,

243
00:20:30,599 --> 00:20:33,240
[SPEAKER_01] s takvim autokratskim modelima

244
00:20:33,240 --> 00:20:34,500
[SPEAKER_01] i autokratskim režimama,

245
00:20:34,500 --> 00:20:36,799
[SPEAKER_01] kao što su u Moskvi i Pekingu,

246
00:20:36,799 --> 00:20:38,539
[SPEAKER_01] i ne možete razvijati tu neku

247
00:20:38,539 --> 00:20:40,220
[SPEAKER_01] ravnopravnu ekonomsku suradnju

248
00:20:40,220 --> 00:20:40,980
[SPEAKER_01] na reciprocitetu.

249
00:20:41,980 --> 00:20:43,059
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ali veliki dio...

250
00:20:43,059 --> 00:20:43,900
[SPEAKER_01] Ne postoji reciprocitet,

251
00:20:43,900 --> 00:20:44,900
[SPEAKER_01] to je problem ozbiljan.

252
00:20:44,900 --> 00:20:46,640
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ne možete imati reciprocitet.

253
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:48,500
[SPEAKER_00] Tako, i to se vidjelo u konačnici

254
00:20:48,500 --> 00:20:49,900
[SPEAKER_00] u odnosu uvoza i izvoza.

255
00:20:49,900 --> 00:20:51,680
[SPEAKER_01] Dugoročno, to uvodi i svukov

256
00:20:51,680 --> 00:20:53,140
[SPEAKER_01] u ekonomskom ratu,

257
00:20:53,140 --> 00:20:54,720
[SPEAKER_01] u kojem sad, na primjer,

258
00:20:54,720 --> 00:20:56,119
[SPEAKER_01] Amerika i Kina imaju vrlo zategnute

259
00:20:56,119 --> 00:20:57,740
[SPEAKER_01] odnose u ekonomske,

260
00:20:57,740 --> 00:20:58,599
[SPEAKER_01] upravo, ili jednostavno,

261
00:20:58,599 --> 00:21:00,859
[SPEAKER_01] imate dva rašta modela

262
00:21:00,859 --> 00:21:01,799
[SPEAKER_01] koje jednostavno ne mogu se,

263
00:21:01,799 --> 00:21:03,980
[SPEAKER_01] ne mogu biti komplementarne.

264
00:21:03,980 --> 00:21:04,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ali s druge strane,

265
00:21:04,940 --> 00:21:07,180
[SPEAKER_00] i ovim sada nategnutim odnosima

266
00:21:07,180 --> 00:21:08,839
[SPEAKER_00] je prethodilo razdoblje

267
00:21:08,839 --> 00:21:10,599
[SPEAKER_00] u kojem su licemjerno

268
00:21:10,599 --> 00:21:12,660
[SPEAKER_00] se Zapad pravio da ne vidi

269
00:21:12,660 --> 00:21:15,220
[SPEAKER_00] kršenja ljudskih prava u Kini,

270
00:21:15,220 --> 00:21:17,380
[SPEAKER_00] kako bi brzo, pohlepno

271
00:21:17,380 --> 00:21:19,460
[SPEAKER_00] zaradili na toj jeftinoj

272
00:21:19,460 --> 00:21:20,279
[SPEAKER_00] radnoj snazi,

273
00:21:20,279 --> 00:21:23,460
[SPEAKER_00] koje u stvari totalno oprimirani ljudi

274
00:21:23,460 --> 00:21:25,160
[SPEAKER_00] koji su radili za malo novaca

275
00:21:25,160 --> 00:21:26,500
[SPEAKER_00] u prelošim uvjetima.

276
00:21:26,500 --> 00:21:28,420
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, u stvari Zapad je,

277
00:21:28,420 --> 00:21:29,460
[SPEAKER_00] kao i sa Ukrajinom,

278
00:21:29,460 --> 00:21:30,779
[SPEAKER_00] u stvari Ukrajina,

279
00:21:30,779 --> 00:21:32,700
[SPEAKER_00] sad se stvara slika kao da je

280
00:21:32,700 --> 00:21:34,619
[SPEAKER_00] cijeli demokratski svijest

281
00:21:34,619 --> 00:21:35,480
[SPEAKER_00] na strani Ukrajine,

282
00:21:35,480 --> 00:21:36,519
[SPEAKER_00] ali do nedavno,

283
00:21:36,519 --> 00:21:37,720
[SPEAKER_00] to uopće nije bilo tako,

284
00:21:37,720 --> 00:21:39,380
[SPEAKER_00] do nedavno Ukrajina uopće

285
00:21:39,380 --> 00:21:40,480
[SPEAKER_00] nije poticana bila

286
00:21:40,480 --> 00:21:42,500
[SPEAKER_00] zbog odnosa sa Rusijom.

287
00:21:42,500 --> 00:21:43,359
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što,

288
00:21:43,359 --> 00:21:45,099
[SPEAKER_01] da se to isto sad bitno kazati

289
00:21:45,099 --> 00:21:47,220
[SPEAKER_01] za ovu našu stranu,

290
00:21:47,220 --> 00:21:48,539
[SPEAKER_01] našu perspektivu koje mi gledamo,

291
00:21:49,019 --> 00:21:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] možda će to uvi pojednostavljeno,

292
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:51,539
[SPEAKER_01] šta ja kažem,

293
00:21:51,539 --> 00:21:52,519
[SPEAKER_01] možda će neki ekonomisti reći

294
00:21:52,519 --> 00:21:54,500
[SPEAKER_01] da ja možda pojednostavljeno stvari,

295
00:21:54,500 --> 00:21:56,779
[SPEAKER_01] ali imam osjećaj

296
00:21:56,779 --> 00:21:58,720
[SPEAKER_01] da je sav taj ekonomski

297
00:21:58,720 --> 00:21:59,900
[SPEAKER_01] prosperitet koji smo vidno žili

298
00:21:59,900 --> 00:22:00,779
[SPEAKER_01] za 30 godina

